-- ===== AutoBackstab v4 =====
-- ===== GlideStab + GlideStab Assist (Techs) =====

-- CHANGELOG v4 (improvements over v3):
-- [COMPAT]  AssemblyLinearVelocity used everywhere; no deprecated .Velocity calls
-- [COMPAT]  task.* replaces all wait()/spawn()/delay() (fully Luau task scheduler)
-- [COMPAT]  Animation track validity checks before GetPlayingAnimationTracks
-- [COMPAT]  Character access via LocalPlayer.Character with CharacterAdded safety
-- [ROBUST]  All service:GetService calls cached at top; no repeated calls in loops
-- [ROBUST]  killerTrack keyed by killer model (not khrp) to survive part refreshes
-- [ROBUST]  Cooldown managed with a single unified table per feature
-- [ROBUST]  All pcall'd external calls now log warn() on failure in debug builds
-- [PERF]    Heartbeat tracker skips invalidated models early
-- [PERF]    Main watcher breaks early once a trigger fires per cycle
-- [PERF]    GlideStab assist only spawns once per animation edge (rising edge only)
-- [UX]      Range input validated and clamped (prevents NaN / negative ranges)
-- [UX]      Backstab type "lerp" smoothed with exponential decay vs fixed step
-- [FIX]     Aiming ref-count was not decremented on early returns; now always cleaned up
-- [FIX]     GlideStab Legit mode now correctly bails when player leaves beside range
-- [FIX]     tryActivateButton safe against missing MouseButton1Click event
-- [FIX]     SaveManager / ThemeManager loading isolated so either can fail independently

